The paper discusses the problem of "dry patches" in software development and proposes a solution for program repair systems to produce an "explainable bug fix." This topic falls under the sub-category of software engineering (cs.SE) as it deals with improving the software development process. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of natural language and controlled language, which relates to programming languages (cs.PL). The use of program repair bots also involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and the paper discusses the larger context of software development, which relates to software design (cs.SD) and machine learning (cs.LG).
